{"tid":178892,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"遇到啲怕人咳既仆街就好玩啦","createTime":"2017-03-30T00:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T03:04:55.000Z","uid":12618,"like":5,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9539656c56ce1e0e56ce5ea29f2e812930133229","tid":178892,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:44:25.000Z","msg":"今日搭西鐵  閪人多就緊<br />\n撞正我咳又撞到閪人真係算你唔好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有條仆街企正我隔離開大個喇叭打機<br />\n我好大力咳左兩聲(無向住佢同我有戴口罩)<br />\n佢即刻行開左少少<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原來佢驚咳  今次好玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n我咳完 佢無反應閂細聲啲<br />\n我再咳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢今次直情用手勃  覺得有菌果隻勃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">都係無閂細聲</span></span><br />\n之後我就望住佢 佢又望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後先施施然收埋部電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到我落車佢都無攞電話出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對付啲仆街真係要仆街過佢至得#<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ab21560f4eaff7df499b0ebb5ac7843b774206","tid":178892,"uid":57410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:47:59.000Z","msg":"樓主做乜鳩<br />\n幾時咳代表叫人較細聲？ 你當佢係電話set左聲控？"},{"pid":"be35a19c49aaa8b85263e3f85d3fa24ac98baf0f","tid":178892,"uid":65234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:48:48.000Z","msg":"屌連登真係好多小學雞"},{"pid":"2cdc640ec43cbcc6c9b1805cad30d6686f7d1019","tid":178892,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:49:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主做乜鳩<br />\n幾時咳代表叫人較細聲？ 你當佢係電話set左聲控？</blockquote><br />\n佢怕咳係佢既事 佢電話game聲成車都聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ecfbb339496228317689bb479d0fad9583fed66","tid":178892,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:51:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌連登真係好多小學雞</blockquote><br />\n電話game聲勁大嘈到人就唔小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad3d1108773f4e14e5fe9ff386a4ddb93f9832c","tid":178892,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:53:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"57d6394049bf6a5d3b2cd8e2d1595c105872e70a","tid":178892,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:55:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戇鳩嗰個係你</blockquote><br />\n戇鳩得過你整肥婆icon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0735aa2d9dd7ae78d18e799dfd4528cda92b924f","tid":178892,"uid":94452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:56:27.000Z","msg":"直接叫人熄細聲啲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你咳都會影響埋其他人"},{"pid":"87bf3794d92e5505117004b30750f9fa77a79b7b","tid":178892,"uid":37447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T00:56:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主做乜鳩<br />\n幾時咳代表叫人較細聲？ 你當佢係電話set左聲控？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2882f92455eb7e0126ca074d29b85a1cdd06b17b","tid":178892,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:00:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直接叫人熄細聲啲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你咳都會影響埋其他人</blockquote><br />\n有戴口罩都影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不如規定病人唔好出街"},{"pid":"2dfb7d0dc750ef8fb7e3b31736df5d5a705c9117","tid":178892,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T01:08:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8d50984930df0b9980575cbe131f50850b57c13","tid":178892,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco